data.description: Welcome home to this oasis in the heart of Boynton. This fabulous pool home is loaded with extras and is perfect for entertaining. Enter into the large open Living Dining Area. The two toned gourmet kitchen has everything you need including stainless appliances, granite and lots of storage. Plenty of bedrooms for the whole family. The large Master is off the enclosed patio which is perfect for family fun. Once you step outside, you will feel at peace in the tranquil mature foliage. Splash around in the pool or relax on the patio while the kids swing on the playground. A true gem.
